title: Carmen McRae - 1998 - The Collected Carmen McRae FLAC
description:
Carmen McRae - 1998 - The Collected Carmen McRae

Although collectors and serious fans will have little use for it, RCA's Collected Carmen McRae is a nice overview of her RCA recordings for casual fans, containing 12 tracks including "Dear Ruby," "It's Magic, " "Dedicated to You, " "Misty, " "Tenderly, " "Lover Man," and "My Old Flame." (AllMusic)
